* “Centennial Memorial of Nakatsu Corps”<ref name="Grounds Overview"/>
* “Kyōji Shinmei Monument”<ref name="Grounds Overview"/>
* “Imperial Accession Memorial”<ref name="Grounds Overview"/>
* “Russo-Japanese War Shell Monument”<ref name="Grounds Overview"/>
* {{ill|Matsuo Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉}} Haiku Monument<ref name="Grounds Overview"/>
