'''Nakatsu Daijingu''' (中津大神宮) and '''Nakatsu Shrine''' (中津神社) are Shinto shrines located in Ni-no-chō, {{ill|Nakatsu|ja|中津市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ōita Prefecture|ja|大分県|12=draft}}. Both shrines hold the status of former village shrines under the pre-modern shrine ranking system.

